            </div>
            <div class="supportOptions">
              <button class="supportTile" type="button"><i class="fa-solid fa-ticket"></i>Booking help<span>Tickets, seats, rooms and schedules</span></button>
              <button class="supportTile" type="button"><i class="fa-solid fa-receipt"></i>Payment issue<span>Receipts, refunds and failed payments</span></button>
              <button class="supportTile" type="button"><i class="fa-solid fa-building"></i>Partner help<span>Listings, staff and dashboards</span></button>
            </div>
